strings: <voice_0x01000E58><se_def>*: Surely it's too dangerous to carry on pursuing this fiend! I mean, look at what he did to Golding...
<voice_0x01000E5A><se_def>*: Interesting... I thought there was no one on this island besides us and Golding's murderer.
<voice_0x01000E5B><se_def>*: Let me give you a piece of advice. Steer clear of the old ruins in the middle of the island.

<voice_0x01000E5C><se_def>*: Ignore me at your peril!
You have been warned.
